This is the ABOUT file.
This file describes this example project.

This example project is simple web shop with following features.

- simple CMS for adding and deleting categories and products
- home page with categories
- categories page with list of products
- product detail page
- adding and removing products to cart
- cart page
- checkout form page
- thankyout page
- orders get saved and can be seen in the CMS

This project is a simple example for the [core](php-mysql-micro-framework-core/blob/master/), [api](php-mysql-micro-framework-api/blob/master/) and [app](php-mysql-micro-framework/blob/master/) micro framework.
